### Login (obtener token JWT)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.access_token); %}

---

### Listar usuarios (solo admin)
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### Crear categoría (admin o moderator)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Programación"
}

---

### Listar categorías
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/categories

---

### Crear post (usuario autenticado)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Primer post",
  "content": "Este es un post de prueba",
  "category_id": 1
}

---

### Listar posts publicados
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/posts

---

### Crear comentario en un post
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Excelente post, gracias!"
}

---

### Listar comentarios de un post
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/comments/1

---

### Eliminar comentario (admin, moderator o autor)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}